│   └── field_extractor.py      ← Config-driven field extraction
├── analyzer/
│   ├── pattern_detector.py     ← Autocorrelation period detection
│   ├── timestamp_detector.py   ← Heuristic Y/M/D scanner
│   ├── structure_analyzer.py   ← Orchestrates → generates suggested config
